               -------------------------------------------------------

1. Start MongoDB
    To start MongoDB, execute from the Command Prompt:

    C:\mongodb\bin\mongod.exe

2. Connect to MongoDB
   COpen another Command Prompt and issue the following command:

   C:\mongodb\bin\mongo.exe
